# Django M2 API Documentation

## Swagger / OpenAPI

- Document every endpoint
- When an endpoint is added or changed, **update Swagger documentation**
- Keep docs in sync with implementation

## Postman

- Postman collection in `postman/` folder
- When an endpoint is added or changed, **update the Postman collection**
